{"tid":1761672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國經濟增長再度提速","createTime":"2019-11-29T05:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T06:37:56.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e5cea48f802c5dc16d889b305bc5155a9d54c10b","tid":1761672,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"美國經濟增長再度提速<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001085329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001085329&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=ec4351b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001085329</a><br />\n<br />\n美國經濟2019年下半年加快擴張步伐，數據顯示，第三季度國內生產總值(GDP)增幅超過最初預期。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國經濟分析局(Bureau of Economic Analysis)對GDP的第二次估算，在截至9月30日的三個月，美國經濟折成年率增長2.1%。高於1.9%的初步預測和第二季度2%的增速。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這一最新的估計、以及表明10月耐用品訂單反彈幅度大於預期的數據，可能有助於緩和人們對美國經濟健康狀況的擔憂，尤其是對製造業和商業投資（繼續受到唐納德&bull;特朗普(Donald Trump)對華貿易戰影響的考驗）的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n這些樂觀的數據對美國股市構成支撐，標普500指數(S&amp;P 500)周三在前一交易日創紀錄收盤高點的基礎上進一步上漲0.42%。美元指數也出現上漲。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「第三季度實際GDP的增長，反映了個人消費支出、聯邦政府支出、住宅投資、私營部門庫存投資、出口以及州政府和地方政府支出的正面貢獻，但被非住宅固定投資的負面貢獻部分抵消，」美國經濟分析局周三表示。<br />\n<br />\n數據還顯示，10月耐用品訂單從5月以來最大降幅的水平反彈。該月耐用品訂單增長0.6%，輕鬆超越華爾街預測的下降0.8%，並標誌著該指標從9月向下修正後的下降1.4%（此前為下降1.2%）水平強勁復甦。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不包括飛機的非軍工資本品訂單&mdash;&mdash;被視為商業投資的指標&mdash;&mdash;較9月向上修後的下降0.5%大幅增加至1.2%。經濟學家們曾預測該指標10月下滑0.3%。<br />\n<br />\n「上月耐用品訂單的增長是由資本品訂單飆漲所推動，表明商業設備投資水平好於預期，」凱投宏觀(Capital Economics)資深美國經濟學家邁克爾&bull;皮爾斯(Michael Pearce)表示。<br />\n<br />\n「總體而言，我們仍預計經濟增長在短期內將進一步放緩，但放緩幅度似乎比我們的最初預期更為溫和，」他補充說。<br />\n<br />\n即使在經濟表現好於預期之後，第四季度之初的價格增長依然疲軟，對美國央行維持低利率的理由提供了支持。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部的數據顯示，10月份核心個人消費支出(PCE)指數&mdash;&mdash;美聯儲(Federal Reserve)官員將該指數（剔除極為波動的食品和能源價格）作為他們的首選通脹指標&mdash;&mdash;同比上漲1.6%，低於前一個月1.7%的漲幅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">凱投宏觀資深美國經濟學家安德魯&bull;亨特(Andrew Hunter)表示，通脹數據「突顯出在可預見的將來不太可能再次加息」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「如果經濟增長像我們預期的那樣放緩，企業的定價能力將會減弱，核心通脹率可能再次開始減速，」諮詢公司MFR首席美國經濟學家喬舒亞&bull;夏皮羅(Joshua Shapiro)表示。<br />\n<br />\n經季節因素調整後，10月美國家庭支出環比增長0.3%，與湯森路透(Thomson Reuters)調查得出的共識預期相符。"},{"pid":"93745fe38bee0170c89a54e071c6f053c0e1fa5b","tid":1761672,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319d71682a141a06a53684210b12474e066bbc77","tid":1761672,"uid":108347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"證明中国反制強而有力，果斷高效....咦等等....."},{"pid":"ecd6a872f928f5982c13fb29495fdd6bda0eff78","tid":1761672,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:22:30.000Z","msg":"deadline fighter 一齊寫聖誕卡畀英國歐洲議員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n拉落去有哂英國address <br />\n依幾日截郵<br />\n幫手寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02bdea9882b36def2e1a3464e0ec2411ad20436","tid":1761672,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"真係make American great <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba139cb20fc69e93cb2e8ae41cbda846160f669","tid":1761672,"uid":169665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"中共啲反制去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682db991da29cb309cc73431e2be46ac15f5a9d1","tid":1761672,"uid":62714,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"痴撚線發達國家2% 增長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c39717cfa5864e2d3f9cd0371e75d44cf53b14e","tid":1761672,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cecf2fca45e227cd804deb37a6d4cdf9207c9d5","tid":1761672,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266648a5defacc84ee57b769bba41e56c57520d8","tid":1761672,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:27:25.000Z","msg":"又話黎緊會跌"},{"pid":"e54355a11bdcd79355e5e54802321c55f0f26ef8","tid":1761672,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"會唔會係伏嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常經濟危機之前盤數都係好靚"},{"pid":"e742337111178e0d817765e10a8f4fa1c75d3c3c","tid":1761672,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c153d594cceda1ce4b1057bc02d2e67c79b6b606","tid":1761672,"uid":14087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quot